## Install

You do not need Loadout to use this skill -- pick whichever section below
matches your setup. The Loadout flow is just a convenience for people who
already manage their skills with it.
{{ if .HasClaude }}
### For Claude

Copy the `claude-build/` directory to `~/.claude/skills/{{ .Name }}/`:

    cp -R claude-build/ ~/.claude/skills/{{ .Name }}/
{{ end }}{{ if .HasCodex }}
### For Codex

Copy the `codex-build/` directory to `~/.codex/skills/{{ .Name }}/`:

    cp -R codex-build/ ~/.codex/skills/{{ .Name }}/
{{ end }}
### With Loadout (optional)

If you use [Loadout](https://github.com/sethdeckard/loadout), import the
`loadout-source/` directory into your shared skills repo:

    loadout import loadout-source/
